## Features

### ✅ Group-level rotation index
The v2.1.0 CHANGELOG described per-group rotation tracking but the 
implementation still used per-category counters. This PR implements it.

**Before (unfair):**
- Ticket on Cat-A (→ Group Support) → Alice (index Cat-A: 0)
- Ticket on Cat-B (→ Group Support) → Alice (index Cat-B: 0) ← duplicate

**After (fair):**
- Ticket on Cat-A (→ Group Support) → Alice (shared Group index: 0)
- Ticket on Cat-B (→ Group Support) → Bob   (shared Group index: 1)

New table `glpi_plugin_roundrobin_rr_groups` stores one rotation index 
per group. Upgrade from 2.x is safe — schema migration runs automatically 
without touching existing `is_active` config.

### ✅ Spanish locale (`es_ES`)
Full translation of all UI strings. Updated `roundrobin.pot` with 
previously missing strings (`No group assigned`, `Config saved`, 
`Config reset`).

