## UI Modernization

Config page rewritten with Bootstrap 5 — the native GLPI 11 component set:

| Before | After |
|---|---|
| `tab_cadre_fixe` HTML table | Bootstrap 5 cards + `table-hover` |
| Radio buttons (enable/disable) | `form-switch` toggles |
| `\|raw` Twig filters (XSS risk) | All output escaped with `\|e` |
| Single monolithic form | Two independent forms (options / categories) |
| Categories without group: broken switch | Disabled `ti-ban` icon with tooltip |
| Member count: plain text | Color badge (green >0, yellow =0) |

